      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to be letting this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and detailed. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or door ding anywhere. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
