    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering linear torque to a Variable M Differential Lock. Meticulously maintained, this example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a factory-fresh suspension geometry that ensures razor-sharp turn-in and communicative feedback. The aesthetic remains in collector-grade state, with the original paint exhibiting deep luster and the interior showing zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key mechanical masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
