    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in what can only be described as showroom-fresh condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting its meticulous garage-kept history. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no signs of wear, and the 'new car' scent still lingers. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function precisely as they did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service record and a whisper-quiet engine that delivers smooth, effortless power. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually untouched specimen that has been pampered by a single enthusiast owner. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a pristine service history.",
      "price": 48500.0,
