    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this car\u2014it\u2019s an absolute gem! It has been incredibly well-loved and is in truly flawless condition. It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home where it\u2019ll be appreciated as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
