    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This collector-grade example is equipped with a 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering tactile engagement through a short-throw shifter. The chassis remains in impeccable condition, with the factory carbon fiber roof reducing the polar moment of inertia for superior turn-in. Crucially, the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells and the throttle actuators have been upgraded, addressing the platform's primary mechanical concerns. The M-Variable differential and Electronic Damping Control (EDC) function flawlessly, ensuring the suspension geometry provides optimal contact patches under high lateral loads. This is a strictly OEM+ preservation for the discerning enthusiast.",
